@startuml
title Viaverse Infrastructure / Deployment Config — Class Model

class ServiceConfig {
  serviceName: String
  imageTag: String
  replicas: Int
  resourceRequests: CpuMem
  resourceLimits: CpuMem
  healthCheckPath: String
  env: Environment
}

class SecretRef {
  name: String
  provider: SecretsManager | KMS
  externalSecretName: String
  rotationPolicy: RotationPolicy
  mountedAs: ENV | FILE
}

class Release {
  id: UUID
  version: String
  gitSha: String
  imageDigest: String
  environment: DEV | STAGE | PROD
  status: ReleaseStatus
  deployedAt: Instant
}

class DbMigration {
  version: String
  serviceName: String
  scriptName: String
  backwardCompatible: Boolean
  status: MigrationStatus
  appliedAt: Instant?
}

class DeploymentPolicy {
  requiresApproval()
  allowsRollback()
  checksMigrationSafety()
  checksErrorBudget()
  checksSecurityScan()
}

class ServiceSLO {
  serviceName: String
  availabilityTarget: Decimal
  latencyTargetMs: Int
  errorBudgetPolicy: String
  alertRuleIds: List<UUID>
}

class BackupPlan {
  resourceType: DB | BUCKET | INDEX
  schedule: String
  retentionDays: Int
  rpoMinutes: Int
  rtoMinutes: Int
  restoreTestedAt: Instant?
}

class InfraEvents {
  ReleaseStarted
  ReleaseSucceeded
  ReleaseRolledBack
  MigrationApplied
  SecretRotated
  BackupFailed
  SloBreached
}

ServiceConfig --> SecretRef : uses
Release ..> ServiceConfig : deploys
Release --> DbMigration : includes
DeploymentPolicy ..> Release : validates
DeploymentPolicy ..> DbMigration : checks
ServiceSLO --> DeploymentPolicy : gates
BackupPlan ..> InfraEvents : emits
Release ..> InfraEvents : emits
SecretRef ..> InfraEvents : rotation emits

note bottom
Environment differences must be declarative and versioned.
Secrets are references, never committed values.
end note
@enduml
